Interview Questions
What is a Protected Route?

A route that only authenticated users can access.

Which React Router component is used for redirection?
<Navigate />
What happens if an unauthorized user accesses a protected route?

They are redirected to the login page.

Why are Protected Routes important?

To secure private pages such as:

Dashboard
Profile
Orders
Settings
